              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "Beam current was measured by a 100% feed-back",
                "       type current integrator. The uncertainty in the",
                "       beam current integration was estimated to be",
                "       3-10%."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "The activity of 7Be was measured more than two",
                "       weeks after irradiation, when the short-lived",
                "       activities had been decayed out. No radioactive",
                "       impurities were observed in the gamma-spectra."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "Chemical separation of beryllium was applied to",
                "       a few targets in each run to eliminate a",
                "       possible interference of other activities and",
                "       obtain the absolute cross sections."
              ]
            }
          ],
